    uttakExWhat:'Maxaa ah canshuurta soo baxinta?',
    uttakExWhatDesc:'Markaa aad soo baxisaa xogta, alaabada ama adeegga ganacsiga oo u qasto isticmaal personal ama aad siiso, waxaa la tixgeliyaa canshuurta siday aad isku ibisay salaaddii reer miiska. Faaidadu waxaa lagu canshuuraa xeerka caadiga ah.',
