    uttakExExc2:'Iska wareejinta ganacsigu (§ 9-7(4)): isticmaalka kalama soo baxan marka la qaatay qofka ku qaata ganacsigu oo wuu sii wada',
    uttakExExc3:'Qaab sayniyaa iska leh (§ 2-38): shirkada kaydka saham ku leh shirkada kale — soo baxinta sahamka siday iska leh ayaa la sayniyaa sahndu',
    uttakExExc4:'Xiriirka kooxda: soo baxinta isku duwow akshonaraha, shirkada ku duwow waxaa ay khuseysa canshuurta soo baxinta',
