    uttakExSource:'Isha: Sharciga canshuurta § 5-2, § 5-3 iyo qaybta 9 (Sharciga-1999-03-26-14). Xisaabiyahadu waa tilmaan oo keliya — la midaasho accountant si loogu naago qiimeyno qaas.',
    utdelingTitle:'Qaabka canshuurta macaashka', utdelingDesc:'Culeysiga canshuurta dhabta ah ee qaybinta faa\'iidada AS iyo ganacsiga shakhsiga',
    utdelingIntro:'Xisaabtanani waxay muujinaysaa culeysiga canshuurta guud marka faa\'iidada loo qaybinayo milkiilaha. <b>AS</b> (qaabka saami-qabaha): canshuurta shirkadda 22% + canshuurta macaashka 37.84% = <b>51.5%</b> heerka dhabta ah. <b>ENK</b> ganacsi shaqsi (qaabka ganacsiga): dakhli caadi ah 22% + caymis bulsho 10.8% + canshuur darajo = ilaa <b>50.6%</b> heerka cidhiidhiga. Mabda\'a is-le\'egyaanta wuxuu xaqiijinayaa in qaabka ganacsiga laftiisu aanay bixin faa\'iido canshuur.<br><br><i style="font-size:12px;opacity:.7">Muuqaalka ENK waa tusaale waxbarasho fudaysan — canshuurta dhabta ah waxaa sidoo kale saameynaya cafiska shaqsiyeed iyo yaraynta ugu yar.</i>',
